{"tid":2397063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[毛漢下個到你]水炮車射有線記者 投訴警察課：警員無過錯","createTime":"2021-02-06T06:24:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-06T06:59:07.000Z","uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4e43ec901f0300e0a824f3c7d739fe8568bb5b82","tid":2397063,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T06:24:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210205/KJUEOPY5FBHELFOMJJPW5QBMDY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210205%2FKJUEOPY5FBHELFOMJJPW5QBMDY%2F&d=ZxGTC5m4wH5D2fXTYNKMIcorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=fb20cb28\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210205%2FKJUEOPY5FBHELFOMJJPW5QBMDY%2F&h=fdc46c80\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210205/KJUEOPY5FBHELFOMJJPW5QBMDY/</a><br />\n<br />\n《有線新聞》指，該台記者當日在中環添華道採訪期間，被警方水炮車噴中藍色催淚水劑，其後投訴警方濫用職權。報道引述投訴警察課回覆指，調查顯示，當時環境混亂，多人佔路及暴力衝擊警方防線，使用催淚水劑驅散符合警方程序及法律條文，故把指控列為「並無過錯」。警方指，已把事件通知有關人員，並作出適當訓示。"},{"pid":"a6366ebde3dc583c1513dc9356d1baf20aa13316","tid":2397063,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T06:35:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />ok 收到"},{"pid":"58064678d950fbed66d019f8ce1df0049f30eabc","tid":2397063,"uid":82532,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T06:36:49.000Z","msg":"故把指控列為「並無過錯」。警方指，已把事件通知有關人員，並作出適當訓示<br />\n冇過錯又要訓示<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?&nbsp;表揚先啱啦下嘩"},{"pid":"24e8b912211ac8a558d002f03f867f67ffd2cf19","tid":2397063,"uid":34577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T06:38:18.000Z","msg":"<code>把指控列為「並無過錯」。警方指，已把事件通知有關人員，並作出適當訓示。</code><br />\n冇錯你又訓示？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f7d0107c1006f84f4e8612e02589d6ea1f16ce9","tid":2397063,"uid":76804,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2